creator: Hiwell Psikoloji
descriptionHtml:
KİMDEN HİZMET ALACAKSINIZ?

Tamamı yüksek lisanslı, süpervizyon alan/almış ve kendi terapisine giden uzman psikologlar bulunan platforma kayıt olarak sizin için en doğru psikolog ile eşleşebilir, ücretsiz ön görüşme yapabilirsiniz.

HANGİ KONULARDA DANIŞMANLIK ALABİLİRSİNİZ?

Platformdaki klinik psikologlar; anksiyete bozukluğu, depresyon, mental problemler, panik atak, ptsd (travma sonrası stres bozukluğu), adhd, bağımlılık, alkol bağımlılığı, ilişki problemleri, cinsellikle ilgili sorunlar, yas, kaygı, strese bağlı problemler, obsesyon, yeme bozuklukları, takıntı, travma sonrası stres bozukluğu, LGBTİ+ (lezbiyen, gey, biseksüel, trans, interseks) bireylerin yaşadıkları problemler, iş hayatındaki problemler, mobbing, tükenmişlik sendromu, gelecek kaygısı, kendini değersiz hissetmek, sosyal fobi konularında profesyonel olarak danışmanlık vermektedirler.

HIWELL SİZİN İÇİN UYGUN MU?

Hayat kalitenizi arttırmak ve daha iyi hissetmek için HiWell sizin için doğru adres olabilir. Hayatınızdaki yolunda gitmeyen sorunlar hakkında, yaşadığınız zor süreçlerle ilgili size destek olabiliriz. Eşleşeceğiniz uzman psikologlardan istediğiniz konuda destek alabilirsiniz. Stres, anksiyete bozukluğu, ilişkiler, depresyon, bağımlılık gibi alanlarda uzmanlaşmış psikologlarımız sizlere destek olabilmek için HiWell ile birlikte çalışıyor.

ONLİNE TERAPİ ETKİLİ MİDİR?

Araştırmalara göre online terapinin depresyon, anksiyete, stres ve panik atak gibi birçok psikolojik rahatsızlıkta etkili olduğu kanıtlanmıştır. Ancak psikoloğunuzun herhangi bir ilaç yazamayacağına ve resmi bir tanı koyamayacağına dikkat çekmek isteriz. Ayrıca, aşağıdaki durumlarda HiWell sizin için uygun değildir:
- Kendinize veya başkasına zarar verme düşüncesi içindeyseniz,
- Acil bir kriz durumu yaşıyorsanız,
- Ciddi bir mental hastalık tanısı almış ve önce psikiyatrik destek almanız önerilmişse.

HIWELL GÜVENLİ Mİ?

- Video seanslarınız kesinlikle kayıt edilmez.
- Kullanıcı bilgileriniz şifrelenerek korunur.
- Ödemeleriniz 256 Bit kriptolanmış ve şifrelenmiş sayfalarda BDDK denetiminde gerçekleştirilir.

KİŞİSEL BİLGİLERİNİZİN GÜVENLİĞİ

Bilgilerinizin gizliliği ve güvenliğiniz bizim için çok önemli. Danışmanlarınızla yapacağınız görüşmeler tamamen sizin ve danışmanınızın arasında kalıyor. Ayrıca, anonim olarak kayıt olabileceğiniz sistemde bilgilerinizi şifrelenmiş şekilde tutuyoruz.

title: Hiwell Online Uzman Psikolog

creator: Hiwell Psikoloji
descriptionHtml:
KİMDEN HİZMET ALACAKSINIZ?

Tamamı yüksek lisanslı, süpervizyon alan/almış ve kendi terapisine giden uzman psikologlar bulunan platforma kayıt olarak sizin için en doğru psikolog ile eşleşebilir, ücretsiz ön görüşme yapabilirsiniz.

HANGİ KONULARDA DANIŞMANLIK ALABİLİRSİNİZ?

Platformdaki klinik psikologlar; anksiyete bozukluğu, depresyon, mental problemler, panik atak, ptsd (travma sonrası stres bozukluğu), adhd, bağımlılık, alkol bağımlılığı, ilişki problemleri, cinsellikle ilgili sorunlar, yas, kaygı, strese bağlı problemler, obsesyon, yeme bozuklukları, takıntı, travma sonrası stres bozukluğu, LGBTİ+ (lezbiyen, gey, biseksüel, trans, interseks) bireylerin yaşadıkları problemler, iş hayatındaki problemler, mobbing, tükenmişlik sendromu, gelecek kaygısı, kendini değersiz hissetmek, sosyal fobi konularında profesyonel olarak danışmanlık vermektedirler.

HIWELL SİZİN İÇİN UYGUN MU?

Hayat kalitenizi arttırmak ve daha iyi hissetmek için HiWell sizin için doğru adres olabilir. Hayatınızdaki yolunda gitmeyen sorunlar hakkında, yaşadığınız zor süreçlerle ilgili size destek olabiliriz. Eşleşeceğiniz uzman psikologlardan istediğiniz konuda destek alabilirsiniz. Stres, anksiyete bozukluğu, ilişkiler, depresyon, bağımlılık gibi alanlarda uzmanlaşmış psikologlarımız sizlere destek olabilmek için HiWell ile birlikte çalışıyor.

ONLİNE TERAPİ ETKİLİ MİDİR?

Ancak psikoloğunuzun herhangi bir ilaç yazamayacağına ve resmi bir tanı koyamayacağına dikkat çekmek isteriz. Ayrıca, aşağıdaki durumlarda HiWell sizin için uygun değildir:
- Kendinize veya başkasına zarar verme düşüncesi içindeyseniz,
- Acil bir kriz durumu yaşıyorsanız,
- Ciddi bir mental hastalık tanısı almış ve önce psikiyatrik destek almanız önerilmişse.

HIWELL GÜVENLİ Mİ?

- Video seanslarınız kesinlikle kayıt edilmez.
- Kullanıcı bilgileriniz şifrelenerek korunur.
- Ödemeleriniz 256 Bit kriptolanmış ve şifrelenmiş sayfalarda BDDK denetiminde gerçekleştirilir.

KİŞİSEL BİLGİLERİNİZİN GÜVENLİĞİ

HANGİ KONULARDA DANIŞMANLIK ALABİLİRSİNİZ?

Platformdaki klinik psikologlar mental problemler hakkında profesyonel olarak danışmanlık vermektedirler.

HIWELL SİZİN İÇİN UYGUN MU?

Hayat kalitenizi arttırmak ve daha iyi hissetmek için HiWell sizin için doğru adres olabilir. Hayatınızdaki yolunda gitmeyen sorunlar hakkında, yaşadığınız zor süreçlerle ilgili size destek olabiliriz. Eşleşeceğiniz uzman psikologlardan istediğiniz konuda destek alabilirsiniz. Stres, anksiyete bozukluğu, ilişkiler, depresyon, bağımlılık gibi alanlarda uzmanlaşmış psikologlarımız sizlere destek olabilmek için HiWell ile birlikte çalışıyor.

ONLİNE TERAPİ ETKİLİ MİDİR?

Araştırmalara göre online terapinin depresyon, anksiyete, stres ve panik atak gibi birçok psikolojik rahatsızlıkta etkili olduğu kanıtlanmıştır. - Kendinize veya başkasına zarar verme düşüncesi içindeyseniz,

- Ciddi bir mental hastalık tanısı almış ve önce psikiyatrik destek almanız önerilmişse.

- Ödemeleriniz 256 Bit kriptolanmış ve şifrelenmiş sayfalarda BDDK denetiminde gerçekleştirilir.

KİŞİSEL BİLGİLERİNİZİN GÜVENLİĞİ

Bilgilerinizin gizliliği ve güvenliğiniz bizim için çok önemli. Danışmanlarınızla yapacağınız görüşmeler tamamen sizin ve danışmanınızın arasında kalıyor. Ayrıca, sistemde bilgilerinizi şifrelenmiş şekilde tutuyoruz.

title: Hiwell Online Uzman Psikolog

creator: Hiwell Teknoloji Anonim Sirketi
descriptionHtml:
Why Online Therapy?
Academic studies and subjective experiences of clients and psychotherapists have played a big part in the acceptance of online therapy's effectiveness in recent years. Numerous scientific studies show that online therapy is as effective as face-to-face therapy.
You can start your therapy process with the most suitable specialist for you. Have your sessions from your home or anywhere you feel comfortable, saving the time you spend in traffic.

Why Hiwell?
- We will match you with the most suitable specialist according to your reasons for starting therapy and other answers you gave while registering.
Thanks to Hiwell, the distance between you and the most suitable specialist is not an obstacle. Our expert therapists have passed an extensive interview process, and they come from various cities and countries. After confirming their competencies, we include the expert specialists on our platform and bring them together with you.
- After matching with the most suitable specialist for you, you can have a free welcoming video call. You can meet your therapist through a welcoming video call and get answers to your questions about the therapy process.
We aim to make therapy accessible to everyone. In addition, you can check the advantageous packages we have included, keeping in mind that the therapy's long-term sustainability is essential through our application.

Specialists with Expertise
- In line with our priority of providing ethical and reliable services, we only have competent specialists on our platform who are experts in their area of expertise.
- Hiwell's expert specialist staff consists of specialists who are qualified psychologists registered with the BPS or HCPC or psychotherapists/counselors accredited with the BACP or UKCP.
- As Hiwell, we provide support in individual (for adults), couple and family, and child & adolescent psychotherapy.
Through our application, you can check your specialist's educational and professional background and meet them with a free 15-minute welcoming video call.
- You can get psychological support on many issues with 50-minute video calls.
We would like to inform you that no psychologist has the authority to make an official diagnosis or prescribe medications. Only a medical doctor has the authority to make a diagnosis and prescribe medication. Please contact the nearest health facility immediately for the following conditions, and do not use Hiwell.
-When thoughts of harming yourself or someone else arise
- When you have suicidal thoughts
- In an emergency crisis
- In cases where drug therapy and a diagnosis are necessary.

Privacy and Security
- There is no audio or video recording of your calls.
-All your information is encrypted, protected, and will not be shared with third parties under any circumstances.
-Your payments are made on encrypted pages with Stripe.

Privacy Policy : https://www.hiwellapp.com/en/privacy-policy
User Agreement : https://www.hiwellapp.com/en/user-agreement

You can contact us anytime!
Contact the Help Center on the application or email hello.uk@hiwellapp.com You can send your questions and feedback via email.
You can also follow us on our social media accounts.
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/hiwell.en/
Linkedin: https://www.linkedin.com/company/hiwell/mycompany/
What's New In This Version
We work hard to make your journey of self-discovery an enjoyable experience. We are making the application more functional day by day so that you can start the therapy process with the best specialist for you at any time. We are here to provide a better user experience with our brand new interface!
descriptionShort: Meet expert therapists online

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: By downloading Hiwell, you can find the best specialist for you and start getting therapy right away from anywhere in the world! Start feeling better with Hiwell today!

title: Hiwell Online Therapy

creator: Hiwell Teknoloji Anonim Sirketi
descriptionHtml:
Why Online Therapy?
Academic studies and subjective experiences of clients and psychotherapists have played a big part in the acceptance of online therapy's effectiveness in recent years. Numerous scientific studies show that online therapy is as effective as face-to-face therapy.
You can start your therapy process with the most suitable specialist for you. Have your sessions from your home or anywhere you feel comfortable, saving the time you spend in traffic.

Why Hiwell?
- We will match you with the most suitable specialist according to your reasons for starting therapy and other answers you gave while registering.
Thanks to Hiwell, the distance between you and the most suitable specialist is not an obstacle. Our expert therapists have passed an extensive interview process, and they come from various cities and countries. After confirming their competencies, we include the expert specialists on our platform and bring them together with you.
- After matching with the most suitable specialist for you, you can have a free welcoming video call. You can meet your therapist through a welcoming video call and get answers to your questions about the therapy process.
We aim to make therapy accessible to everyone. In addition, you can check the advantageous packages we have included, keeping in mind that the therapy's long-term sustainability is essential through our application.

Specialists with Expertise
- In line with our priority of providing ethical and reliable services, we only have competent specialists on our platform who are experts in their area of expertise.
- Hiwell's expert specialist staff consists of specialists who are qualified psychologists registered with the BPS or HCPC or psychotherapists/counselors accredited with the BACP or UKCP.
- As Hiwell, we provide support in individual (for adults), couple and family, and child & adolescent psychotherapy.
Through our application, you can check your specialist's educational and professional background and meet them with a free 15-minute welcoming video call.
- You can get psychological support on many issues with 50-minute video calls.
We would like to inform you that no psychologist has the authority to make an official diagnosis or prescribe medications. Only a medical doctor has the authority to make a diagnosis and prescribe medication. Please contact the nearest health facility immediately for the following conditions, and do not use Hiwell.
-When thoughts of harming yourself or someone else arise
- When you have suicidal thoughts
- In an emergency crisis
- In cases where drug therapy and a diagnosis are necessary.

Privacy and Security
- There is no audio or video recording of your calls.
-All your information is encrypted, protected, and will not be shared with third parties under any circumstances.
-Your payments are made on encrypted pages with Stripe.

Privacy Policy : https://www.hiwellapp.com/en/privacy-policy
User Agreement : https://www.hiwellapp.com/en/user-agreement

You can contact us anytime!
Contact the Help Center on the application or email hello.uk@hiwellapp.com You can send your questions and feedback via email.
You can also follow us on our social media accounts.
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/hiwell.en/
Linkedin: https://www.linkedin.com/company/hiwell/mycompany/
What's New In This Version
We work hard to make your journey of self-discovery an enjoyable experience. We are making the application more functional day by day so that you can start the therapy process with the best specialist for you at any time. We are here to provide a better user experience with our brand new interface!

title: Hiwell Online Therapy

creator: Hiwell Teknoloji Anonim Sirketi
descriptionHtml:
Hiwell is the preferred online therapy platform for more than 100.000 people. Powered by licensed and registered psychotherapists and counselors, we offer research-backed psychotherapy modalities for anxiety, stress, depression, relationship & work problems, and other mental health and wellness needs. Hiwell's therapists are experts in Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT), Dynamic Therapy, Interpersonal Therapy, Schema Therapy, and others.

To ensure 100% privacy and confidentiality, we use peer-to-peer encryption for all meetings. No sessions can be viewed or recorded by a third party. Even the payments are processed on encrypted pages.

Why Online Therapy?

Numerous scientific studies show that online therapy is as effective as face-to-face therapy in decreasing the symptoms of anxiety, depression, stress, and other mental health problems. Online therapy is also effective in increasing the quality of life, mental wellness, and psychological wellbeing. Furthermore the users of online therapy report higher satisfaction due to the ease of conducting the sessions online in some scientific studies.

Start your online therapy from your home or anywhere you feel comfortable, saving time and money you spend in traffic while dealing with anxiety, stress, depression and other mental health problems.

Why Hiwell?

Hiwell only hires licensed and registered experts after an extensive vetting and interviewing process. Psychotherapists are evaluated based on their supervision and performance during their time at Hiwell. You can find detailed information about psychotherapists on our website.

Our advanced algorithm matches you with the best therapist based on your needs, expectations, reasons for starting therapy, and schedule based on the questions you answer while registering.

We offer %100 privacy and confidentiality with the peer-to-peer technology used in the video calls. This way only you and your therapist can view the therapy session and no one else.

After getting matched with the most suitable therapist, you can have a 15-minute free-of-charge video call with them to test the suitability yourself and ask your questions about the therapy process. If you are unhappy with the match, you can change your therapist and get another 15-minute free-of-charge video call.

Our mission is to make therapy accessible to everyone. To that aim, we are offering therapy services at the best prices and quality simultaneously. We offer discounted packages for multiple sessions, believing that the long-term sustainability of therapy is essential for solidifying the benefits.

We provide 50-minute psychotherapy and counseling sessions for adults, couples, children, and adolescents.


Disclaimer:

You should seek medical treatment if you are thinking of harming yourself or someone else, you have suicidal thoughts, you are in an emergency crisis or if you are looking for drug therapy or a medical diagnosis.

We would like to inform you that mental health professionals such as therapists, counselors, or clinical psychologists do not have the authority to make an official diagnosis or prescribe medications. Only a medical doctor has that authority. Don't hesitate to contact the nearest health facility immediately for the above-written conditions.


Contact Details

You can send your questions and feedback by contacting Help Center on the application or sending an email to hello@hiwellapp.com.

You can also follow our social media accounts:

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/hiwell.uk/
LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/company/hiwell/
descriptionShort: Start Online Therapy for anxiety, stress, depression & other mental health needs

• We made improvements for bug fixes.

Hiwell's therapists are experts in Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT), Dynamic Therapy, Interpersonal Therapy, Schema Therapy, and other psychotherapy modalities.

To ensure 100% confidentiality and privacy, we use peer-to-peer encryption for all virtual therapy sessions. No sessions can be viewed or recorded by a third party. Even the payments are processed on encrypted pages.

Why Online Therapy?

Numerous scientific studies show that online therapy is as effective as face-to-face therapy in decreasing the symptoms of anxiety, depression, stress, and other mental health problems. Our online therapists offer psychotherapy for anxiety relief, depression help, and stress reduction. Online therapy is also shown to be effective in increasing the quality of life, mental wellness, and psychological wellbeing. Furthermore, the users of online therapy report higher satisfaction due to the ease of conducting the therapy sessions online.

Start your online therapy journey from your home or anywhere you feel comfortable, saving time and money you spend in traffic while dealing with anxiety, stress, depression, and other mental health problems. Prioritize your psychology and mental wellbeing today! If you need to vent your feelings, you can vent to a professional therapist who will listen without judging you.

Why Hiwell?

• Hiwell only hires licensed and registered experts after an extensive vetting and interviewing process. Psychotherapists are evaluated based on their supervision and performance during their time at Hiwell. You can find detailed information about psychotherapists on our website.

• Seamlessly find a therapist that perfectly suits your needs. Our advanced algorithm matches you with the best therapist based on your needs, expectations, reasons for starting therapy, and schedule based on the questions you answer while registering.

• We offer %100 privacy and confidentiality with the peer-to-peer technology used in the video calls. This way only you and your therapist can view the therapy session and no one else.

• After getting matched with the most suitable therapist, you can have a 15-minute free-of-charge video call with them to test the suitability yourself and ask your questions about the therapy process. If you are unhappy with the match, you can change your therapist and get another 15-minute free-of-charge video call.

• Our mission is to make therapy accessible to everyone. To that aim, we are offering therapy services at the best prices and quality simultaneously. We offer discounted packages for multiple sessions, believing that the long-term sustainability of therapy is essential for solidifying the benefits.

• We provide 50-min psychotherapy and counseling sessions for adults, couples, children, and adolescents with expert child, couple, adolescent therapists and marriage counselors.

Disclaimer

You should seek medical treatment if you are thinking of harming yourself or someone else, you have suicidal thoughts, you are in an emergency crisis or if you are looking for drug therapy or a medical diagnosis. We inform you that mental health professionals such as therapists, counselors, or psychologists do not have the authority to make an official diagnosis or prescribe medications.

Hiwell is the preferred online therapy platform for more than 100.000 people. Powered by licensed and registered psychotherapists and counselors, we offer research-backed psychotherapy modalities for anxiety, stress, depression, relationship & work problems, and other mental health and wellness needs. Hiwell's therapists are experts in Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT), Dynamic Therapy, Interpersonal Therapy, Schema Therapy, and other psychotherapy modalities.

To ensure 100% confidentiality and privacy, we use peer-to-peer encryption for all virtual therapy sessions. No sessions can be viewed or recorded by a third party. Even the payments are processed on encrypted pages.

Why Online Therapy?

Numerous scientific studies show that online therapy is as effective as face-to-face therapy in decreasing the symptoms of anxiety, depression, stress, and other mental health problems. Our online therapists offer psychotherapy for anxiety relief, depression help, and stress reduction. Online therapy is also shown to be effective in increasing the quality of life, mental wellness, and psychological wellbeing. Furthermore, the users of online therapy report higher satisfaction due to the ease of conducting the therapy sessions online.

Start your online therapy journey from your home or anywhere you feel comfortable, saving time and money you spend in traffic while dealing with anxiety, stress, depression, and other mental health problems. Prioritize your psychology and mental wellbeing today! If you need to vent your feelings, you can vent to a professional therapist who will listen without judging you.

Why Hiwell?

• Hiwell only hires licensed and registered experts after an extensive vetting and interviewing process. Psychotherapists are evaluated based on their supervision and performance during their time at Hiwell. You can find detailed information about psychotherapists on our website.

• Seamlessly find a therapist that perfectly suits your needs. Our advanced algorithm matches you with the best therapist based on your needs, expectations, reasons for starting therapy, and schedule based on the questions you answer while registering.

• We offer %100 privacy and confidentiality with the peer-to-peer technology used in the video calls. This way only you and your therapist can view the therapy session and no one else.

• After getting matched with the most suitable therapist, you can have a 15-minute free-of-charge video call with them to test the suitability yourself and ask your questions about the therapy process. If you are unhappy with the match, you can change your therapist and get another 15-minute free-of-charge video call.

• Our mission is to make therapy accessible to everyone. To that aim, we are offering therapy services at the best prices and quality simultaneously. We offer discounted packages for multiple sessions, believing that the long-term sustainability of therapy is essential for solidifying the benefits.

• We provide 50-min psychotherapy and counseling sessions for adults, couples, children, and adolescents with expert child, couple, adolescent therapists and marriage counselors.

Disclaimer

You should seek medical treatment if you are thinking of harming yourself or someone else, you have suicidal thoughts, you are in an emergency crisis or if you are looking for drug therapy or a medical diagnosis. We inform you that mental health professionals such as therapists, counselors, or psychologists do not have the authority to make an official diagnosis or prescribe medications.

Contact Details

You can send your questions by contacting Help Center or sending an email to hello@hiwellapp.com.

You can also follow our social media accounts:

www.instagram.com/hiwell.therapy
www.linkedin.com/company/hiwell

Hiwell's therapists are experts in Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT), Dynamic Therapy, Interpersonal Therapy, Schema Therapy, and others.

All therapy sessions are 100% confidential and secure. None of the therapy sessions can be viewed or recorded by a third party. All payments are processed on encrypted pages.

Why Online Therapy?

Numerous scientific studies show that online therapy is as effective as face-to-face therapy in increasing the quality of life and decreasing the symptoms of anxiety, depression, stress, sleep problems, sexual problems, and other psychological issues. Also, the users of online therapy report higher satisfaction and well-being due to the ease of conducting the sessions online.

Start your online therapy journey from your home or anywhere you feel comfortable, saving time and money you spend in traffic while dealing with anxiety, stress, depression, and other mental health problems. Prioritize your psychology and mental well-being today! If you need to vent your feelings, you can vent to a professional therapist who will listen without judging you.

Why Hiwell?

• Hiwell only hires licensed and registered experts after extensive vetting and interviewing. Psychotherapists are evaluated based on their supervision and performance at Hiwell. You can find detailed information about psychotherapists on our website.

• Seamlessly find a therapist that perfectly suits your needs. Our advanced algorithm matches you with the best therapist based on your needs, expectations, reasons for starting therapy, and schedule based on the questions you answer while registering.

• We offer %100 private and confidential video calls. This way, only you and your therapist can view the therapy session.

• After getting matched with the most suitable therapist, you can have a 15-minute free-of-charge video call with them to test the suitability yourself and ask your questions about the therapy process. If you are unhappy with the match, you can change your therapist and get another 15-minute free-of-charge video call.

• Our mission is to make therapy accessible to everyone. To that aim, we simultaneously offer therapy services at the best prices and quality. We offer discounted packages for multiple sessions, believing that the long-term sustainability of therapy is essential for solidifying the benefits.

• We provide 50-min psychotherapy and counseling sessions for adults, couples, children, and adolescents with expert child, couple, adolescent therapists, and marriage counselors.

Disclaimer

You should seek medical treatment if you are thinking of harming yourself or someone else, you have suicidal thoughts, you are in an emergency crisis or if you are looking for drug therapy or a medical diagnosis. We inform you that mental health professionals such as therapists, counselors, or psychologists do not have the authority to make an official diagnosis or prescribe medications.

Contact Details

You can send your questions by contacting the Help Center or emailing hello@hiwellapp.com.

You can also follow our social media accounts:

Why Hiwell?

• Hiwell only hires licensed and registered experts after extensive vetting and interviewing. Psychotherapists are evaluated based on their supervision and performance at Hiwell. You can find detailed information about psychotherapists on our website.

• We offer %100 private and confidential video calls. This way, only you and your therapist can view the therapy session.

Powered by licensed and registered psychotherapists and counselors, we offer research-backed psychotherapy modalities for anxiety, stress, depression, sleep problems, sexual problems, relationship & work problems, and other mental health and well-being needs. Hiwell's therapists are experts in Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT), Dynamic Therapy, Interpersonal Therapy, Schema Therapy, and others.

All therapy sessions are 100% confidential and secure. None of the therapy sessions can be viewed or recorded by a third party. All payments are processed on encrypted pages.

Why Online Therapy?

Numerous scientific studies show that online therapy is as effective as face-to-face therapy in increasing the quality of life and decreasing the symptoms of anxiety, depression, stress, sleep problems, sexual problems, and other psychological issues. Also, the users of online therapy report higher satisfaction and well-being due to the ease of conducting the sessions online.

Start your online therapy journey from your home or anywhere you feel comfortable, saving time and money you spend in traffic while dealing with anxiety, stress, depression, and other mental health problems. Prioritize your psychology and mental well-being today! If you need to vent your feelings, you can vent to a professional therapist who will listen without judging you.

Why Hiwell?

• Hiwell only hires licensed and registered experts after extensive vetting and interviewing. Psychotherapists are evaluated based on their supervision and performance at Hiwell. You can find detailed information about psychotherapists on our website.

• Seamlessly find a therapist that perfectly suits your needs. Our advanced algorithm matches you with the best therapist based on your needs, expectations, reasons for starting therapy, and schedule based on the questions you answer while registering.

• We offer %100 private and confidential video calls. This way, only you and your therapist can view the therapy session.

• After getting matched with the most suitable therapist, you can have a 15-minute free-of-charge video call with them to test the suitability yourself and ask your questions about the therapy process. If you are unhappy with the match, you can change your therapist and get another 15-minute free-of-charge video call.

• Our mission is to make therapy accessible to everyone. To that aim, we simultaneously offer therapy services at the best prices and quality. We offer discounted packages for multiple sessions, believing that the long-term sustainability of therapy is essential for solidifying the benefits.

• We provide 50-min psychotherapy and counseling sessions for adults, couples, children, and adolescents with expert child, couple, adolescent therapists, and marriage counselors.

Disclaimer

You should seek medical treatment if you are thinking of harming yourself or someone else, you have suicidal thoughts, you are in an emergency crisis or if you are looking for drug therapy or a medical diagnosis. We inform you that mental health professionals such as therapists, counselors, or psychologists do not have the authority to make an official diagnosis or prescribe medications.

Contact Details

You can send your questions by contacting the Help Center or emailing hello@hiwellapp.com.

You can also follow our social media accounts:

www.linkedin.com/company/hiwell
